<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family: sans-serif; color: #111; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 16px;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Reset your password</h2>
    <p style="color: #555;">Someone requested a password reset for your Life OS account (<%= @resource.email %>).</p>
    <p style="color: #555;">If this was you, click the button below. The link expires in 6 hours.</p>

    <a href="<%= @reset_url %>"
       style="display: inline-block; margin: 24px 0; padding: 12px 24px; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;">
      Reset password
    </a>

    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 13px;">If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p style="color: #bbb; font-size: 12px;">Or copy this link: <%= @reset_url %></p>
  </body>
</html>
